1195
00:40:36,839 --> 00:40:37,839
What does Wu's family

1196
00:40:37,839 --> 00:40:38,880
have to do with us?

1197
00:40:45,120 --> 00:40:46,159
An, please...

1198
00:40:46,679 --> 00:40:47,520
Stop it,

1199
00:40:47,520 --> 00:40:48,839
I'm not my dad.

1200
00:40:49,400 --> 00:40:50,239
Seriously.

1201
00:40:51,639 --> 00:40:52,520
Well,

1202
00:40:53,359 --> 00:40:54,279
I just wish for the Xu's

1203
00:40:54,279 --> 00:40:56,199
household registration

1204
00:40:56,400 --> 00:40:58,359
to carry on.

1205
00:40:58,359 --> 00:40:58,960
Xin and I

1206
00:40:58,960 --> 00:41:00,199
are not on the registration booklet?

1207
00:41:00,199 --> 00:41:01,880
But the registration would end after you.

1208
00:41:01,880 --> 00:41:02,920
Whose fault is that?

1209
00:41:04,480 --> 00:41:05,679
It's not my fault.

1210
00:41:05,679 --> 00:41:06,920
It's your dad.

1211
00:41:07,040 --> 00:41:07,520
Fine,

1212
00:41:07,520 --> 00:41:08,839
then ask my dad to talk to me.

1213
00:41:09,239 --> 00:41:09,719
Dad,

1214
00:41:11,040 --> 00:41:12,440
come on in, let's talk.

1215
00:41:13,839 --> 00:41:14,239
No, no.

1216
00:41:14,239 --> 00:41:14,839
This...

1217
00:41:15,040 --> 00:41:16,319
None of your business.

1218
00:41:16,679 --> 00:41:17,520
It's fine.

1219
00:41:17,520 --> 00:41:18,480
Step aside.

1220
00:41:22,199 --> 00:41:23,279
Quite confident.

1221
00:41:24,040 --> 00:41:25,199
Taking it all on?

1222
00:41:26,359 --> 00:41:27,520
No...

1223
00:41:29,080 --> 00:41:30,520
I know what you're thinking.

1224
00:41:32,000 --> 00:41:33,040
You feel like

1225
00:41:33,040 --> 00:41:34,440
you've let my dad down

1226
00:41:34,440 --> 00:41:35,839
by not giving him a son, right?

1227
00:41:37,920 --> 00:41:38,719
How does that

1228
00:41:38,719 --> 00:41:40,560
concern us?

1229
00:41:41,440 --> 00:41:43,319
I'll be serious with you now.

1230
00:41:43,480 --> 00:41:44,359
This matter

1231
00:41:44,359 --> 00:41:45,400
ends here.

1232
00:41:45,440 --> 00:41:46,839
Don't mention it to anyone,

1233
00:41:46,839 --> 00:41:47,920
especially Li Lin and Yunjie.

1234
00:41:48,000 --> 00:41:48,880
If you bring it up again,

1235
00:41:48,880 --> 00:41:50,239
I'll really get angry. Got it?

1236
00:41:52,639 --> 00:41:54,520
Can't we discuss it?

1237
00:41:54,520 --> 00:41:55,520
No way.

1238
00:41:56,080 --> 00:41:56,600
Sit properly.

1239
00:41:59,440 --> 00:42:01,239
What's wrong with you?

1240
00:42:08,120 --> 00:42:09,639
You mustn't give my dad a hard time later.

1241
00:42:20,080 --> 00:42:21,000
Did you see

1242
00:42:21,000 --> 00:42:22,520
her attitude just now?

1243
00:42:22,920 --> 00:42:24,440
She was so harsh,

1244
00:42:24,440 --> 00:42:26,120
leaving no room for negotiation.

1245
00:42:26,920 --> 00:42:27,759
What's wrong with the surname Xu?

1246
00:42:27,759 --> 00:42:29,040
She bears the surname Xu as well.

1247
00:42:29,239 --> 00:42:30,159
Isn't that a good thing?

1248
00:42:30,159 --> 00:42:32,000
She should be supporting us.

1249
00:42:32,000 --> 00:42:32,520
Why is she...

1250
00:42:33,159 --> 00:42:34,839
She's been like this,

1251
00:42:34,960 --> 00:42:36,000
always against me.

1252
00:42:36,199 --> 00:42:37,480
Did I raise a daughter

1253
00:42:37,480 --> 00:42:38,920
or a mother?

1254
00:42:39,080 --> 00:42:39,719
Gosh.

1255
00:42:40,359 --> 00:42:41,199
Am I right?

1256
00:42:42,040 --> 00:42:43,880
You're right.

1257
00:42:44,759 --> 00:42:46,719
She's your child. Why get angry?

1258
00:42:48,000 --> 00:42:48,839
It's not about anger.

1259
00:42:48,839 --> 00:42:50,239
This is for

1260
00:42:50,239 --> 00:42:51,920
the Xu family's good.

1261
00:42:51,920 --> 00:42:52,839
Isn't it?

1262
00:42:52,839 --> 00:42:54,520
Why is she so stubborn?

1263
00:42:54,520 --> 00:42:55,080
You see...

1264
00:42:55,359 --> 00:42:56,120
You didn't see

1265
00:42:56,120 --> 00:42:57,279
her attitude.

1266
00:42:58,159 --> 00:42:58,839
Looks like...

1267
00:42:59,199 --> 00:43:00,239
What did she say?

1268
00:43:01,239 --> 00:43:02,040
She said,

1269
00:43:02,159 --> 00:43:03,839
"No way. Don't even think about it."

1270
00:43:04,319 --> 00:43:05,480
"It's impossible."

1271
00:43:06,000 --> 00:43:07,560
That firm attitude.

1272
00:43:08,040 --> 00:43:08,839
Oh my.

1273
00:43:09,239 --> 00:43:11,040
I just don't understand.

1274
00:43:13,000 --> 00:43:14,239
Listen,

1275
00:43:14,319 --> 00:43:15,120
Lili,

1276
00:43:15,600 --> 00:43:17,279
actually, it's my fault.

1277
00:43:18,480 --> 00:43:19,440
I always say to you

1278
00:43:19,440 --> 00:43:20,839
how excellent

1279
00:43:20,839 --> 00:43:22,920
my brother's sons are.

1280
00:43:23,239 --> 00:43:24,040
I wasn't saying it

1281
00:43:24,040 --> 00:43:25,279
for you to hear.

1282
00:43:26,920 --> 00:43:27,639
Isn't it nice

1283
00:43:28,040 --> 00:43:28,920
to have two children,

1284
00:43:28,920 --> 00:43:30,319
one surnamed Xu

1285
00:43:30,319 --> 00:43:31,120
and the other Li?

1286
00:43:31,120 --> 00:43:32,799
It's perfect.

1287
00:43:33,279 --> 00:43:35,080
Why is she overreacting like that?

1288
00:43:35,839 --> 00:43:37,639
Yeah, you are right.

